title: WeHo TV, "Mazer Tour", Angela Brinskele
creator: WEHO TV News
description: Quick tour of the Mazer Archives 2013. The June Mazer Lesbian Archives of Los Angeles  and Southern California houses almost a century of lesbian and feminist artwork, manuscripts, books, records, newspapers, magazines, photographs, games, organizational papers, tapes, letters, scrapbooks, clothing, and flyers.
